[normal]Charles Nelson[bold]: There is always going to be the challenge with the particular way that this transmission occurs.  A lot of the cases where this happens are extremely remote.  It is along the borders and you can see the hotspots.  Interestingly, there are over 500 different types of resistance that have now been identified.  It is not just one that has been travelling; it has been different sorts of resistance developing along borders.  It is in migrant populations and it is in the hardest
[normal]&#x2011;
[normal]to
